15:T462,This is clearly a product family representing Meril's portfolio of absorbable surgical sutures. Internal brochure description aligns perfectly with external tier1_manufacturer evidence showing Meril manufactures multiple absorbable suture products (Filapron monofilament, Megasorb Plus PGA). The generic nature (no specific brand name, just 'Absorbable Sutures') confirms this is a family-level page encompassing multiple SKU variants. External evidence enriches understanding with specific examples: Filapron (monofilament) and Megasorb Plus (braided PGA with chlorhexidine coating). Material specification is validated as synthetic polymers (specifically PGA mentioned) or natural materials. Absorption mechanisms (enzymatic degradation, hydrolysis) confirmed. Marked for review due to: (1) ambiguity_reason flags brand_missing - this family page may need child product pages for specific branded lines like Filapron and Megasorb Plus, and (2) current_confidence=0 suggests initial uncertainty that has now been resolved but warrants stakeholder confirmation of family-level vs. product-level catalog structure decision.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Absorbable Sutures\",\"description\":\"Sutures that break down naturally in the body over time through enzymatic degradation or hydrolysis. Provides temporary wound support during critical healing phase.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Sutures\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",n